INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1367,1,'2025-03-17 11:04:00','2025-03-17 11:04:00','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Palo Alto Networks: The CNAPP pioneer continues to lead the market.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Palo Alto Networks, the pioneer in cloud-native application protection platforms (CNAPPs), delivers the most comprehensive Code to Cloud platform in the world.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As the No. 1 CNAPP by market share, Palo Alto Networks continues to define the category through relentless innovation. The platform delivers end-to-end visibility, proactive threat prevention and seamless security across every stage of the development lifecycle – from code creation to cloud deployment and runtime operations. GigaOm has further validated Palo Alto Networks leadership in their inaugural CNAPP Radar report, recognizing Palo Alto Networks unmatched vision and commitment to securing the future of cloud-native environments.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Read the report to learn:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Which capabilities should be considered differentiators when choosing a CNAPP vendor.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>What emerging features will have an impact on the market in the next 12 to 18 months.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>What sets Palo Alto Networks apart from other solutions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>“Palo Alto Networks excels in a number of areas, all of which scored a 5/5. Its CIEM capabilities are excellent, offering net-effective permission calculations, least privilege recommendations, and just-in-time access control.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button {\"width\":25,\"className\